snippet.title: Blood Running - Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
🎉The Blood Running Closed Alpha is here! This has been 6 months in the making, and I'm super excited for you guys to finally get your hands on it.

🚨Play the Blood Running Alpha Demo
https://www.bloodrunning.com/demo

👉Join Our Discord
https://discord.gg/dead-unicorn-772603203246227547

Blood Running is a stylish extraction shooter where you'll enter the cyber-wasteland, collect blood for your clients, loot valuable gear, and venture into the remnants of a world in ruins.
